comment: Allen (IND) jumps from point A to B and makes contact with Wall (WAS) that affects his layup attempt.
West (IND) cleanly strips the ball from Wall (WAS) on the drive to the basket.
Gortat (WAS) cleanly blocks the layup attempt by Hill (IND).
West (IND) makes contact with Butler's (WAS) arm and the contact affects his play to the basket.
Butler (WAS) commits a take foul on Miles (IND).
Even though Hill stops when contact occurs, Gortat (WAS) grabs Hill's (IND) arm while setting the screen, interfering with his ability to close out on the shooter.
